      "text": [
        " قَالَ أَبُو عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ع یَا مُفَضَّلُ إِنَّهُ مَنْ تَعَرَّضَ لِسُلْطَانٍ جَائِرٍ فَأَصَابَتْهُ بَلِیَّهٌ لَمْ یُؤْجَرْ عَلَیْهَا وَ لَمْ یُرْزَقِ التَّصَبُّرَ عَلَیْهَا."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
          "1.  Imam  Ja’far  Sadiq  (a.s.)  said,  “O  Mufaddal!  One  who clashes with an oppressive ruler without any cause, will not be saved in his bad times and even his patience will not serve him as his sustenance.”"
        ]
      }
